  "description": "The refrigerator was created in the Side by Side form factor. A distinctive feature of the model is the increased working space. So, the useful volume of the model is excellent 508 liters. Under the refrigeration zone, 334 liters are allotted, and the freezing chamber holds 174 liters. The compartments are located vertically, and not one above the other, as in conventional models. Refrigerator Gorenje NRS 918 EMB operates on the basis of a single compressor with an inverter device. In this case, two separate circulation circuits are used. Management is electronic. The convenient, clear and reliable SensoTech touch panel is used. Refrigerator and freezer have 5 shelves and 2 drawers. The door of the refrigerator compartment received 3 shelves. The freezer door has 4 shelves. Both cameras have LED lighting. The freezer compartment is equipped with an ice maker. Ice cubes are dispensed by turning the knob. The productivity of the freezing zone reaches 11 kg/day. Electricity consumption is 321 kWh/year. The model can remind you of an open door, for this a sound signal is provided. The chillers and freezers use the NoFrost Plus system. A MultiFlow 360° cold flow distribution system is also provided.",
